race.comment: STAHNADO (5) made an eye-catching return when just missed in a richer race at Pakenham fresh. Claim helps and fitter again. Back in this company looks hard to beat with a repeat performance, NEROLA (4) also has returned from a break in good order, settling last but coming with a barnstorming run to score. Has upside and fitter again so worth following up. JUST REMEMBER IT (1) just missed fresh then was safely held latest but in tougher grade. Is a third-up winner and can do much better this line-up. MYSTERY BLONDE (8) is better than the last two runs. Placed only try course and distance and can improve here. BOOM BOOM BETTY (6) is much better than latest and this easier. Rating from the fresh-up run augers well for this.
